newsitem.title: USA: CBOT overnight Project A ag volume 856 contracts.
newsitem.headline: CBOT overnight Project A ag volume 856 contracts.

text.p: Chicago Board of Trade said its Project A overnight agricultural trading volume totaled 856 contracts compared with 407 overnight Thursday.
There were 18 wheat, 185 corn, 524 soybean, 119 soymeal, one soyoil, three oat and six soybean calls traded.
In overnight trading, wheat was 3/4 cent lower to one cent higher, corn was one cent lower to 1/4 cent higher and soybeans were one to 4-1/4 cents higher.
